{"tid":756523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美駐中國大使館附近傳爆炸　疑男子丟爆裂物失敗自炸","createTime":"2018-07-26T06:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T02:21:41.000Z","uid":66943,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7d9394916b96401dca51ed8d99dccfcd2cf77d64","tid":756523,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:32:15.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n位於北京朝陽區的美國駐中國大使館稍早傳出發生爆炸，使館附近已拉起封鎖線，目前傷亡未明。<br />\n<br />\n有網友宣稱，疑似是一名男子想對大使館丟擲爆裂物，但丟擲失敗，炸傷自己。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n網路上也流傳多部影片，可以看見現場煙霧迷漫，已拉起封鎖線，眾多公安正在處理。<br />\n<br />\n另外，也有住在北京的網友表示，「吃完飯走在街上聽到一聲巨響，然後美國大使館附近開始拉警戒線了。」「好幾個街區外就聽到爆炸聲了！」<br />\n<br />\n▼網上流傳多張照片，大使館附近冒出白煙。（圖／翻攝微博，下同。）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/142932_5d8edd0522cfad679b6f841db10e8298.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F142932_5d8edd0522cfad679b6f841db10e8298.png&h=7ad32177&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"513f6a92042bc4b6cbcec526455810d9f3ad550b","tid":756523,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:33:25.000Z","msg":"宣戰啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31f037d56c366286c2c9512335edebc91ead6ec6","tid":756523,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"92169c8e674552fd42807402238cce6bbb176a11","tid":756523,"uid":5686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:35:00.000Z","msg":"俾佢掉到入去就真係開戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1787bc6b5437d0d022f06120ff122542bf8cab","tid":756523,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31f037d56c366286c2c9512335edebc91ead6ec6","tid":756523,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T06:33:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2